  "DP.564.0091": "Roark: Hey! [0103,0000]!\nIs this maybe your first time here?\\f\nWelcome to Sinnoh’s Underground!\\f\nHuh? Where is this, you ask?\nDoesn’t the Radar make it obvious?\\f\nThis is a giant underground network\nof passages underneath Sinnoh.\\f\nHuh? What am I doing down in this\nexpanse of a place?\\f\nThat’s kind of hard to answer.\\f\nI mean, you can do pretty much\nanything you want down here.\\f\nFor instance, you can dig up Treasure,\nSpheres, and make a Secret Base.\\f\nYou can play with your friends down\nhere, too.\\f\nYou should talk to the Underground\nMan in Eterna City.\\f\nI have to get going now.\nI’ll see you around!"
